  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/InputSignalWithTransform\", \"name\": \"InputSignalWithTransform\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/packages/core/src/authoring/input/input_signal.ts#L55-L84\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"inputsignalwithtransform\">InputSignalWithTransform<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#inputsignalwithtransform\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label dev-preview\" title=\"This API is in Developer Preview\">\n      <a href=\"guide/releases#developer-preview\">developer preview</a>\n    </label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p><code><a href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform\" class=\"code-anchor\">InputSignalWithTransform</a></code> represents a special <code><a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a></code> for a\ndirective/component input with a <code>transform</code> function.</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#description\">See more...</a></p>\n  </section><section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform\" class=\"code-anchor\">InputSignalWithTransform</a>&#x3C;T, TransformT> extends <a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a>&#x3C;T> {\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  <div class=\"descendants interface\">\n    <h2 id=\"child-interfaces\">Child interfaces<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#child-interfaces\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <code><a href=\"api/core/InputSignal\" class=\"code-anchor\">InputSignal</a></code>\n    \n  </li>\n</ul>\n  </div>\n\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">See also<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/core/InputSignal\"><code>InputSignal</code></a>\n<p> for additional information.</p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>Signal inputs with transforms capture an extra generic for their transform write\ntype. Transforms can expand the accepted bound values for an input while ensuring\nvalue retrievals of the signal input are still matching the generic input type.</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nclass MyDir {\n  disabled = input(false, {\n    transform: (v: string|boolean) => convertToBoolean(v),\n  }); // <a href=\"api/core/InputSignalWithTransform\" class=\"code-anchor\">InputSignalWithTransform</a>&#x3C;boolean, string|boolean>\n\n  click() {\n    this.disabled() // always returns a `boolean`.\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n  \n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/InputFunction\n - api/core/InputSignal\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/InputSignal\n - api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#child-interfaces\n - api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#description\n - api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#inputsignalwithtransform\n - api/core/InputSignalWithTransform#see-also\n - api/core/Signal\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/packages/core/src/authoring/input/input_signal.ts#L55-L84\n-->"
